1
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:17,720
This...

2
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:18,920
This costume...

3
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,320
Why is it here?

4
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,040
Madam Bai again.

5
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:24,440
Chunxing.

6
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,640
Where is Master Lin?

7
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:31,640
Come.

8
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,480
Chunxing.

9
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,480
Don't be afraid.

10
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,640
The Inspector is asking you a question.

11
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:37,680
Where is Master Lin?

12
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,480
Master...

13
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,840
After Master saw Steward Lai,

14
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,960
he fainted.

15
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,560
Ashun has already taken him back to his room

16
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,160
to rest.

17
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,680
I think...

18
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,040
I smell that same fragrance again.

19
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:12,680
This...

20
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,000
This is the scent on him.

21
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,640
Was Steward Lai the only one

22
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,560
here earlier?

23
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,360
Who found his body first?

24
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,120
I don't know

25
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,040
if Steward Lai was here alone.

26
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,080
I only know

27
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,200
that Master and Ashun found Steward Lai.

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,600
It's so late.

29
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,120
Why did Master Lin come to the mourning hall?

30
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,600
After Old Madam died,

31
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,160
Master comes here every night

32
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,240
to kneel before Old Madam's spirit tablet for a while,

33
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,640
and then burn some joss paper for her

34
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,560
before going to rest.

35
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:40,960
However,

36
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,720
he came a bit later today.

37
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,280
That's why...

38
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,160
Have you found the cause of death?

39
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,360
Preliminarily,

40
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,000
he was force-fed

41
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,880
a high concentration of arsenic.

42
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,720
He experienced immense pain

43
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:57,840
before he died.

44
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,680
I found this in his hand.

45
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,240
He was holding it very tightly.

46
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,720
It must be something

47
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,840
important.

48
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,400
What is this?

49
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,200
I don't know.

50
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:19,840
Chunxing,

51
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,920
where is Steward Lai's room?

52
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,120
Diagonally opposite Judou and Chunxiao's room.

53
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,160
Okay.

54
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,400
Find someone

55
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,760
to settle Steward Lai's body first.

56
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,760
Go quickly.

57
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,160
Yes.

58
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,200
Okay.

59
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,800
Where did you send him?

60
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,360
A steward's room...

61
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,360
Why is it so clean and tidy?

62
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,840
I'm asking why you sent Chuncheng away.

63
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,960
What did you tell him to do?

64
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,080
Didn't Master Lin faint?

65
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,040
I asked him to go check on him.

66
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:18,680
I remember now.

67
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,480
Before Old Madam died,

68
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,240
she called Judou and Steward Lai

69
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,720
to her room

70
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,000
and talked for a while.

71
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,960
Steward Lai's face was flushed red

72
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,440
when he came out of Old Madam's room,

73
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,000
and he even knocked over

74
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,680
the tea I brewed for Old Madam.

75
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,080
Later,

76
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,520
Judou also came out crying

77
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,960
and ran out of Old Madam's room.

78
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:40,880
I say,

79
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,080
Huang Jinrong,

80
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,440
what are you holding?

81
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,800
A chrysanthemum.

82
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:55,320
Judou.

83
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,640
Are you saying

84
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,920
this is Judou's personal belonging?

85
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,880
It seems Laifu and Judou had an affair.

86
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,880
After Old Madam Lin found out,

87
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,280
she called them both to her room.

88
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,600
That's why Chunxing saw

89
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:17,200
Judou crying and packing her bags.

90
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,040
I don't get it.

91
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,040
Then,

92
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:23,320
even if Old Madam Lin wanted to kick them out,

93
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,680
what does it have to do with the case?

94
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,720
We still need more evidence.

95
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,520
Wait for me.

96
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,640
Questioning them all night.

97
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,280
I'm exhausted.

98
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,400
But at least

99
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,520
it wasn't in vain.

100
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,200
Yeah.

101
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,200
In the Lin family's account books,

102
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,520
even though there are only torn pages,

103
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:51,880
yesterday,

104
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,440
I checked them with the accountant.

105
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,160
The missing parts

106
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,040
basically

107
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,840
all show Laifu's debts.

108
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:58,960
Then,

109
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,480
could Laifu have embezzled the funds?

110
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,280
He used his position

111
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,960
to embezzle some valuables

112
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:05,960
for

113
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,320
his secret meetings with Judou.

114
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,320
Buying precious items

115
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,640
to win Judou's favor.

116
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,200
Seems like spending so much time with me

117
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,360
has made you smarter.

118
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:20,080
A shrewd person like Old Madam Lin

119
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,160
must have

120
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,600
kept a close eye on the finances.

121
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,720
Combined with her knowledge of the servants,

122
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:25,800
she discovered

123
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:26,760
Laifu

124
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,240
and Judou's affair.

125
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,560
Laifu,

126
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,840
you've been in the Lin estate for years.

127
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,920
I believe I've treated you well.

128
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,560
How could you do such

129
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,880
a scandalous thing?

130
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,920
And you,

131
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,000
Judou.

132
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,760
As a maid,

133
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,720
you have no shame.

134
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,640
To have an affair with Laifu!

135
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,680
Old Madam,

136
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,280
I know I was wrong.

137
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,760
But Laifu and I

138
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,600
truly love each other.

139
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,440
Shut up!

140
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,520
In this Lin estate,

141
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,440
how dare you be so insolent!

142
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,600
Laifu,

143
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,040
as the steward,

144
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,800
you dared to use your position

145
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,040
to embezzle the Lin family's valuables,

146
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,480
just to please this woman!

147
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,280
Do you know what crime this is?

148
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,400
Old Madam,

149
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,480
I...

150
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,520
I had a moment of folly.

151
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,840
I was blinded by foolishness.

152
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,520
Please spare my life, Old Madam!

153
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,400
Doing such a disgraceful thing,

154
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,160
and you still want me to spare you?

155
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,640
The reputation of my Lin estate,

156
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,320
how can I let you trample on it?

157
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,000
Get out of the Lin family immediately!

158
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,040
Don't let me see you again.

159
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,040
You disgust me.

160
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,200
So it seems

161
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,640
Laifu is indeed the prime suspect.

162
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,040
It's just a pity

163
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,600
that he and Judou are already dead.

164
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,760
I suppose

165
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,000
it was destined

166
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:52,680
by fate.

167
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,440
I've been looking everywhere for you.

168
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,200
Guess what?

169
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:56,960
Master Lin is awake.

170
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,080
He's waiting for you.

171
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:01,960
Judou, Chunxiao,

172
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,600
and the Second Madam...

173
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,920
They all died so bizarrely.

174
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,520
Yes, indeed.

175
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,080
This couldn't possibly be the work of a human.

176
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:06,960
It must be Madam Bai.

177
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:07,520
Right.

178
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,320
It's Madam Bai.

179
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,400
Her vengeful spirit lingers.

180
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,280
She used the ghost costume to take their lives.

181
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,160
Will she come for our lives too?

182
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,840
What should we do?

183
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,000
Everyone,

184
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,640
do not let this nonsense

185
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,520
cloud your judgment.

186
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,160
Master Lin.

187
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,840
The so-called ghost costume taking lives

188
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,080
is nothing but the killer

189
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,000
trying to create a diversion

190
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,160
and cover their tracks.

191
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,080
That's easy to say,

192
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,800
but you don't even know who the killer is.

193
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:33,520
No.

194
00:08:34,800 --> 00:08:35,720
I know who it is.

195
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,080
He knows?

196
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:37,680
Everyone,

197
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,560
these are Judou's personal belongings

198
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:40,920
found in Laifu's room.

199
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:42,680
We suspect

200
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,240
that Laifu and Judou

201
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,280
were having an affair.

202
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,480
And this ledger

203
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,920
records all the details

204
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:51,120
of Laifu stealing the Lin family's property.

205
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:51,760
Look, Master Lin.

206
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,120
I believe Old Madam Lin

207
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,760
discovered Laifu and Judou's affair,

208
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,400
which is why Laifu silenced her.

209
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:01,960
Are you saying

210
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,920
my mother was killed by Laifu?

211
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,480
But if

212
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,320
Steward Lai is really the killer,

213
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,200
then who

214
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,800
killed him now?

215
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,560
Could it be

216
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,960
that Madam Bai is really taking lives?

217
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,560
Madam Bai taking lives?

218
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,480
Although every murder

219
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,880
seems to have been carefully staged,

220
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,520
a goose leaves a trace when it flies,

221
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,680
and water leaves ripples when it flows.

222
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,720
If it were truly a vengeful spirit taking lives,

223
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,120
why use poison to kill?

224
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,240
I have examined Laifu's body,

225
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,800
and it can be confirmed

226
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,080
that Laifu

227
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,360
was forced to drink arsenic

228
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:33,920
and died from it.

229
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,120
Arsenic?

230
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,160
Furthermore,

231
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,400
Laifu also left us a piece of evidence

232
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,120
that can identify the killer.

233
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,440
The stitching on this pouch is so rough.

234
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,520
It doesn't look like something from my household.

235
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,680
Could it be the work of an outsider?

236
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:56,760
As for this,

237
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,200
we will be responsible for investigating it.

238
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,280
Master Lin,

239
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,760
from now on,

240
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,800
please close your doors to guests.

241
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,800
No one in the household is allowed to leave

242
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,040
until the killer is found.
